###INICIO CONFIGURACIONES GENERICAS###

######INICIO CONFIGURACION REDIRECCIONES######
RewriteEngine On
RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^www\. [NC]
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://inveliagroup.com/$1 [L,R=301]
Redirect 301 /inveliagroup.com https://inveliagroup.com/
Redirect 301 www.inveliagroup.com https://inveliagroup.com/
######FIN DE CONFIGURACION REDIRECCIONES######

###FIN DE CONFIGURACIONES GENERICAS###

###FIN HTDINA###

